{"tid":131793,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大愈唔出聲愈似異類","createTime":"2017-02-23T10:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T12:55:28.000Z","uid":19145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74972fad723594df96150be3a905b787b3431694","tid":131793,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:08:57.000Z","msg":"有時係覺得講野好攰 寧願聽人講都唔想自已講<br />\n但d人就好似覺得一定要乜都一撚嘴咁講一餐先正常<br />\n要同d唔了解自已既人相處真係好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc79f8dbf016ac50daff71d455a11dd721aa7421","tid":131793,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e9ac6bd2d0079df87c35adf2ae7d09fc765c58","tid":131793,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:13:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed3c81476c40084f81429c73fe12cc78426f0575","tid":131793,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/181332_4b0de9fb052bf88e59dbc341ce384089.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F181332_4b0de9fb052bf88e59dbc341ce384089.jpg&h=ddd2f5c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67b3947de992b2b5fb829dd3bd5721e2d1644c00","tid":131793,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:13:36.000Z","msg":"懶得出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09408664350b60d800bb50e859e1a1aa4563f29","tid":131793,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋人愈大愈悶毒，自己問題定係香港消磨咗自己?</blockquote><br />\n我對朋友其實好d<br />\n但其他人真係懶d出聲 係咁搵話題r偈傾仲辛苦過唔出聲"},{"pid":"0b10d118abc5aba5b745e1e66a9ef85b30afd934","tid":131793,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/181332_4b0de9fb052bf88e59dbc341ce384089.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F181332_4b0de9fb052bf88e59dbc341ce384089.jpg&h=ddd2f5c1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個都想be itself 但係有時其他人d眼光or俾到自已既感覺真係好擾人"},{"pid":"9cbfeecf2c9113d643c63e2c6260c8c0e4c9ce55","tid":131793,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff37df22b2fdcab79a12d9154e0474625fde3d24","tid":131793,"uid":72575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:21:04.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前會乜都講一餐 講好多on9野都唔理<br />\n識到好多朋友 個段時間係最開心<br />\n唔知點解大左就好似搵唔到話題同人傾<br />\n又成日做話題終結者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n群體活動還好，但同人獨處嘅時候好多dead air"},{"pid":"7960a0a7610d2d6bdb78d09e4e9f786ee7fce511","tid":131793,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:23:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前會乜都講一餐 講好多on9野都唔理<br />\n識到好多朋友 個段時間係最開心<br />\n唔知點解大左就好似搵唔到話題同人傾<br />\n又成日做話題終結者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n群體活動還好，但同人獨處嘅時候好多dead air</blockquote><br />\n你好似係真係因為長大而沉默<br />\n但我自已好似係骨子裡有好多時都唔想出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9920cc70dfee44efaf9d2b1b104130f491cde1a8","tid":131793,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb42fd84f7516cf1acfecdce6b03e25dcf5f15b0","tid":131793,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8815c074a063248395328666a511937af84c8202","tid":131793,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84515139015a166d2d05c838a4d371896ab3c54d","tid":131793,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27e05d41f59d5ba8154c23938d6a39b24ec9f2c","tid":131793,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:23:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d9fae974097071bdaf9ae7e25f2ec837d0a99d7","tid":131793,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T12:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前會乜都講一餐 講好多on9野都唔理<br />\n識到好多朋友 個段時間係最開心<br />\n唔知點解大左就好似搵唔到話題同人傾<br />\n又成日做話題終結者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n群體活動還好，但同人獨處嘅時候好多dead air</blockquote><br />\n你好似係真係因為長大而沉默<br />\n但我自已好似係骨子裡有好多時都唔想出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係連以前中意打機呢樣興趣都冇咗</blockquote><br />\n唉 今日個人病病地 思想都跟住病"}]}